T1  - Gains in bank mergers: Evidence from the bond markets
AU  - Penas, Marı́a Fabiana
AU  - Unal, Haluk
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 74
IS  - 1
SP  - 149
EP  - 179
